snippet: A sore foot was the main problem noted in President Obama’s latest physical, which found him likely to remain healthy “for the duration of his presidency.”
abstract: Results of Pres Obama's latest physical examination reveal that his biggest problem is foot pain, due to the amount of time he spends on his feet.
lead_paragraph: A sore foot was the main problem noted in President Obama’s latest physical, which found him likely to remain healthy “for the duration of his presidency.”

headline.main: Obama’s Checkup: Healthy, but Ouch, That Right Foot
headline.print_headline: Obama’s Physical Exam Turns Up a Small Problem: Foot Pain
